{
  "stem": "2004.1",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My name is Max Durst.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was born on January the 9th, 1927 in Cieszyn, Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Cieszyn was a part-- is a city in a region of Poland which was known as Silesia.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Our town was basically the border between Poland and Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Our part of the town had a population of approximately 20,000.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had a river that ran between the Polish and Czech sides.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The name of the river was the Olza.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was a bridge whereby-- which separated the two countries.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And of course, we could-- being residents of the Polish side of Cieszyn, we could, by special pass, cross over to the Czech side of Cieszyn.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Most of my family, my father's family, lived on the Czech side of Cieszyn.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Therefore, we practically were every day, my family and myself, in the Czech side.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But of course, we lived on the Polish side.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Are you-- are you referring to family people or just people in general?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, some of the family people that lived in Poland, of course, they sort of chosen to live in Poland.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was because they lived in the Poland-- in the Polish side before World War I.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they remained in that part.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, Poland and Czechoslovakia were created shortly after World War I.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as far as the population, I don't think that the Polish and Czech populations were particularly fond of each other.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were sort of-- they're both Slavic countries, but not particularly friendly to each other.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Each side had a gripe about the other.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We as Jews didn't particularly take part in it because we lived very well.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, we got along very well with the Jewish population of from the Czech side.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
